thread.title: BRIEF-FBL Financial Group Q4 Non-GAAP Operating Earnings Per Share $0.99

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-FBL Financial Group Q4 Non-GAAP Operating Earnings Per Share $0.99
text:
Feb 8 (Reuters) - FBL Financial Group Inc:
* FBL FINANCIAL GROUP REPORTS FOURTH QUARTER AND FULL YEAR 2017 RESULTS
* Q4 NON-GAAP OPERATING EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.99 * Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE $4.33 * Q4 EPS REFLECTS A ONE-TIME BENEFIT FROM TAX CUTS AND JOBS ACT OF 2017 ENACTED DECEMBER 22, 2017 OF $85.8 MILLION
* QTRLY TOTAL REVENUE $183 MILLION VERSUS $184.2 MILLION * “WELL POSITIONED AS WE MOVE FORWARD IN 2018” Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
